Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:10.11,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Have you heard of Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:13.90,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,She was in the ninth grade, class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:16.61,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Was there someone \Nnamed Misaki in class 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:19.31,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,It happened 26 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:23.28,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,She'd been popular \Nsince the seventh grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:26.69,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,She was smart, pretty, \Nand had a great personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:30.92,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Both the teachers and \Nstudents adored her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:34.38,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,There's always someone \Nlike that in every grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.59,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,But shortly after \Nstarting the ninth grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:38.89,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Misaki died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:40.72,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.47,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,I heard it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:46.14,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Of course, everyone \Nwas completely shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:48.57,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Until someone said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:50.52,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Said what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:53.81,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,He pointed to \NMisaki's desk and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:57.99,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,"Misaki's not dead. \NShe's right there."{"Misaki's right there. She's not dead."}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:00:59.82,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,And that was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:02.20,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Well, it was just an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:08.29,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,But since then, class 3 continued\Nto act as if Misaki was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.21,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,That's kinda creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:15.03,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,They continued the \Nact until graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:15.01,Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnWC Mano Negra Bta\c&H0D0406&\3c&H0D0406&\bord0.7\fsp1\be1\fs72\pos(521,436)}Do Not Enter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:19.72,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,The principal even arranged to have Misaki's\Nseat included in their graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:21.39,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Isn't that a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:23.72,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,If that were the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:27.10,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:30.27,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,The rest of the story is...
