Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:42.28,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,How are you feeling? \NDoes it still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:44.20,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:49.16,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,My, what a way to \Nstart your life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:51.70,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:53.00,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.17,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:58.38,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,Goodness, no. \NDon't you worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:01:59.59,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,You couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:02.05,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Um, does my father know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:03.76,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,I haven't told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:07.18,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,Yousuke is in India \Nright now, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:10.47,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Want me to tell him? \NI have his number.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:14.73,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,No, thank you. \NI'll call him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:17.27,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,That's probably best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:22.32,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,That Yousuke, \Nhe's such a dutiful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:26.20,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,In all this time \Nsince Ritsuko died...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:31.04,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,That's the Yomiyama River flowing \Nthrough the center of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:33.79,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Can you see the \Ngrounds beyond it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:35.41,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.38,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You mean that building?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.25,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.92,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,That's the school \Nyou'll be attending.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:46.13,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Is that the same school \Nyou went to, Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:49.22,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Yep. That was \N14 years ago, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:50.89,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,So my mother went there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:51.69,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.48,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,My sister, Ritsuko, \Nwent to Yomi North, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:55.81,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yomi North?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:58.02,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Yomiyama North Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:02:58.86,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:02.19,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Public schools and \Nprivate schools differ a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:04.32,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,but it just takes \Nsome getting used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.61,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll get \Nused to it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:09.07,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:10.62,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.29,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Once you're out of the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.54,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I'll help you prepare \Nfor life at Yomi North.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:21.34,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Oh! Now you're reading a novel by\NStephen King, mister horror lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:28.59,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,Well, I'll leave you guys alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:37.94,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,We're ninth grade students in class 3\N of Yomiyama North Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:39.60,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:43.27,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,I'm Kazami. Kazami Tomohiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:44.94,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,This is Sakuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:48.86,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. \NI'm Sakuragi Yukari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:49.61,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,And this is—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:51.20,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Akazawa Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:55.75,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Did you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.91,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:04:00.67,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Sakuragi and I are class officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:03.21,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Akazawa is in charge \Nof countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:06.51,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,We're here today as \Nrepresentatives of class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.47,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Countermeasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.30,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You just transferred here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:15.81,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,We heard you were starting school on Monday, but that you suddenly fell ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:20.73,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,So we decided to visit you \Non behalf of the entire class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:23.40,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Here. These are from all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.53,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,You're from Tokyo, right?{You moved here from Tokyo, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.36,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:31.32,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,And you attended \Na private school there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:33.28,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Why did you transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:35.37,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,For family reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:40.24,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Is this your first time \Nliving in Yomiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.00,Default,Kouchi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:46.59,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Oh. I figured that \Nyou used to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:48.51,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I've visited before,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.88,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,but I've never lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.51,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,How long did you visit for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:53.59,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:55.64,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:58.47,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I was still young, \Nso... maybe a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:03.98,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:07.70,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,I've copied the notes from \Nthe start of the first term.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.82,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:12.95,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I think my first day will \Nbe after Golden Week,{OR: early May}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:13.95,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,so I'll see you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:19.20,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Um, Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:20.41,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:22.58,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:24.38,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Sakakiba—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.96,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Your first name's Kouichi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:28.84,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,May we call you Kouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.88,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:36.51,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,We look forward to getting \Nto know you, Kouichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:40.85,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Same here. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:54.41,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Are you sure you haven't lived\Nin Yomiyama before, Kouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:59.24,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:10.96,Sign,Phone,0,0,0,,{\c&H394033&\b0\fnpixelmix\fs48\pos(694,317)}Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.48,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,P-Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:56.09,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Are you a student at Yomi North?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:02.68,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Do you have something to do \Non the second basement level?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:04.89,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:07.85,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,But the second basement level is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.61,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm delivering something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.49,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,My poor other half...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:19.49,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,...is waiting for me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.51,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:49.56,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.12,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.08,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Misaki Mei.
