Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:36.36,Default,Bird,0,0,0,,Good morning, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:39.35,Default,Bird,0,0,0,,Good morning, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:41.82,Default,Bird,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.28,Default,Bird,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:45.70,Default,Bird,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:51.92,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,Good morning! How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:53.46,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.29,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,It's two in the morning over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.71,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,India's hot as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.30,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.22,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,You start school today, don't you?{You're about to leave for school, aren't you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.34,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,I'm calling to wish you \Ngood luck. Be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:04.76,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:05.85,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,How you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.22,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,How're things since you \Ngot out of the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:11.06,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Kouichi? I wanted to say—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.52,Alternative,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hang on. The signal's bad over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:17.32,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I'm feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.86,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:21.57,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,Yeah, pneumothorax \Nisn't the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:23.86,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,I had one when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.95,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Really? I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.66,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,I never told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:30.62,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,I didn't want anyone \Ntelling you it's hereditary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.46,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:36.46,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,I actually had it twice, \Nbut never again after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:38.67,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,So if it's hereditary, \Nyou're all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.21,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I sure hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:42.63,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,Just think of it as \Nsomething that's in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.64,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,and go enjoy your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.39,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I won't let it bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:50.22,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,Thatta boy! Remember to tell\Nyour grandparents that I said hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:52.60,Default,Yousuke,0,0,0,,Man, India is seriously hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:02.57,Default,Bird,0,0,0,,Good morning, Rei! \NGood morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.86,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Rei is {\i1}your{\i0\fsp7} {\r}name, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.49,Default,Bird,0,0,0,,Cheer— Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.74,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Sure. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:17.67,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Moving along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:20.38,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,The third thing you need to know \Nto prepare yourself for Yomi North is:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:23.67,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Always uphold the class rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:24.88,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:28.05,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Things might be \Ndifferent in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:31.06,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,but here in Yomiyama, the group \Nmatters more than the individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:33.73,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I think I can handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:34.81,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:37.98,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Now, the fourth thing \Nyou need to know is—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:39.06,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kouichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:42.44,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,Breakfast is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:45.74,Default,Ryouhei,0,0,0,,She said, "Breakfast is ready", Kouichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.20,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Good morning, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.29,Default,Ryouhei,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:54.20,Default,Ryouhei,0,0,0,,Are you going back \Nto the hospital today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:56.17,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,No, I've been discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.21,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I start school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:00.42,Default,Ryouhei,0,0,0,,Ah, school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:03.76,Default,Ryouhei,0,0,0,,You're already in \Njunior high, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.67,Default,Ryouhei,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:08.18,Default,Ryouhei,0,0,0,,Must be good to be young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.72,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I'm in the ninth grade now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.10,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I'll be in high school next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:16.51,Default,Ryouhei,0,0,0,,If only that hadn't \Nhappened to Ritsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:20.15,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,Kouichi! Go eat your breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.40,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:23.86,Alternative,Bird,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why, Rei? {\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:29.57,Default,Kubo,0,0,0,,I hope you'll be able to \Nget along with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:32.66,Default,Kubo,0,0,0,,If you have any troubles at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:35.08,Default,Kubo,0,0,0,,please don't hesitate to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:40.00,Default,Kubo,0,0,0,,You can also talk to Ms. Mikami, \Nthe assistant homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.25,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:44.67,Default,Mikami,0,0,0,,We look forward to \Nhaving you with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.42,Sign,Board,0,0,0,,{\fnEraserDust\b0\c&HB9B5B1&\blur0.6\fry-13\b0\fay-0.15\fs72\frz1.481\pos(546,92)}May 6 (Wed.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:57.18,Sign,Board,0,0,0,,{\b0\blur0.6\b0\fs32\fnJake Bitch Dude\pos(813,65)\c&H656363&}Kouichi Sakakibara
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:57.19,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I moved here because \Nof my father's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:00.40,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I'm living with my grandparents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:03.82,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,And, um... it's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:11.28,Default,Kubo,0,0,0,,Please give our new \Nfriend a warm welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:14.69,Default,Kubo,0,0,0,,Help out each other, \Nand work hard together,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:20.71,Default,Kubo,0,0,0,,so that you can all graduate \Nin prime health next March.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:25.30,Default,Kubo,0,0,0,,You can take that seat \Nover there, Sakakibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.17,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.03,Default,Ouji,0,0,0,,Are you better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:50.03,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yes, I feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:52.16,Default,Saruta,0,0,0,,How does this town \Ncompare to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.53,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,It's not that different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:56.20,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,But Tokyo sounds so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:59.96,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Rural areas like Yomiyama have\Nnothing going for them these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.21,Default,Teshy,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.96,Default,Teshy,0,0,0,,Nothing interesting \Nhappens here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.34,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Tokyo has its downsides, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.71,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,It's so noisy, you can't relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:10.59,Default,Saruta,0,0,0,,I guess it might seem that \Nway, if you've lived there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:11.97,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.97,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,I'd love to live in Tokyo!{I'd love to try living in Tokyo!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:17.26,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I like it better here. \NIt's much quieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.60,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You're surrounded by nature, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:21.73,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,That's something you'd \Nonly hear from a Tokyoite.{That's something you'd only hear from soneone who lives in Tokyo.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:24.56,Default,Ouji,0,0,0,,I heard your dad is \Na college professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.98,Default,Ouji,0,0,0,,And that he's currently doing\Nresearch in a foreign country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.73,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.40,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Everyone knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:32.36,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Mr. Kubodera told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:34.62,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I see. Did he mention \Nmy old school, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:37.03,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Pretty much everyone knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:39.24,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Ms. Mikami talked to us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:39.99,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:44.12,Default,Teshy,0,0,0,,Sucks that Ms. Mikami \Nisn't our homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:46.50,Default,Teshy,0,0,0,,She's beautiful, {\i1}and{\i0\fsp5} {\r}she has a hot body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:48.55,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:52.88,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Oh? You're not into \Npretty women, Kouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.09,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:57.14,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,What kind of girls are\Nyou into, Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:58.47,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:01.35,Default,Ouji,0,0,0,,By the way, what country \Nis your dad in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:02.10,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,India.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.23,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Spring marks his first year there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.81,Default,Ouji,0,0,0,,India, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:07.77,Default,Teshy,0,0,0,,I bet it's hot there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:10.19,Default,Teshy,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to \Ndo it. I hate the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:11.61,Default,Saruta,0,0,0,,Consider yourself lucky, Teshy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:14.91,Default,Saruta,0,0,0,,No matter how hard you try, you're never gonna do research in a place like India.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.28,Default,Teshy,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! I'm well aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:25.12,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,What's wrong? \NIs something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:27.04,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:29.42,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,But I was wondering about \Nthe other girl who visited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:31.30,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Akazawa, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.51,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Is she absent today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:34.93,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Yeah, looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:40.31,Default,Teshy,0,0,0,,Hey! Why don't we give you a \Ntour of the school during lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.72,Default,Teshy,0,0,0,,It's tough not knowing \Nwhere stuff is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:43.35,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Good idea. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:45.10,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.77,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.82,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.33,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,You look like you want to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:09.38,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yeah. I love running.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.84,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.38,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,So, you've run before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:15.26,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Um, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:19.93,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I hear you have \Na heart condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.51,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,I was born with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:25.23,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,so I don't know what \Nit feels like to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:30.15,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,I wish I could run \Nwith all my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:33.90,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You might be able to someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:40.49,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right. \NMaybe someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.71,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:52.50,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,...go to the nurse's \Noffice to lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:53.25,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:54.67,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:56.59,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,I can get there by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.10,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:07.39,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Where did Takabayashi go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.90,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,To rest in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:12.48,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:19.07,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,I fell yesterday and \Nsprained my ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:23.58,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,We don't have gym \Nwith another class?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.24,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Only class 3 is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:30.58,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Classes 1 and 2, and classes \N4 and 5, have gym together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:37.05,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,You walked around during lunch with \NKazami, Teshigawara, and the others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:37.71,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:41.34,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Did they say anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:43.26,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,They just gave me \Na tour of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:44.26,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:45.10,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:48.86,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:52.60,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,If we're not careful, \NAkazawa will yell at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:16:59.03,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hey, Sakuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:16:59.86,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.07,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I've been wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:03.24,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Where's Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:09.54,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,The girl named Misaki Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.08,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You know, the one wearing\Nan eyepatch on her left eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:17.96,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I didn't see her in \Nthe classroom at lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:31.02,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.67,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hey, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:56.38,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You're watching gym class, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.26,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Are you allowed to be up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.68,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:08.10,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,But there's no point in \Nwatching from up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:12.64,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,And you? Are you \Nallowed up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:15.40,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:19.23,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Were you drawing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:27.49,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,How do you write "Mei"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:30.41,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,With the character \Nthat means "cry".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:33.83,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,The same character used \Nin "resonate" and "scream".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:35.29,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:40.00,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,So, do you remember meeting me \Nat Yomiyama Hospital the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.30,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,In the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.55,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You got off at the \Nsecond basement level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.60,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.93,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What did you go to the \Nsecond basement level for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:54.94,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You said you were \Ndelivering something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.15,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You were holding \Nsome kind of white doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:57.98,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Is that what you were deliver—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:00.40,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Might be. I hate being questioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:02.07,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.11,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to \Nforce you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.24,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I just, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:12.29,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Something very sad \Nhappened that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:19.92,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You are Sakakibara Kouichi, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:20.84,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.88,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Your classmates \Nhaven't told you yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.30,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Told me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:29.39,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,They associate \Nyour name with death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:32.22,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,But not just any death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:37.89,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,A cruel, irrational death \Nthat took place at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:42.82,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,This school is in a \Nplace close to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:45.28,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,especially the \Nninth grade's class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:49.70,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It's much, much closer to it \Nthan any of the other classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:52.58,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,To... death?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:57.21,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You really don't know \Nanything, Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:19:59.92,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Nothing at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:02.84,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Nobody has told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.30,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.92,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You'll find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.55,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You shouldn't try \Nto get close to me.
